list.comment: Adds implementations for DAO-s. Tested. Adds Hibernate second level cache functionality. Changes data source from Hikari to C3P0 as connection leaks was detected. Adds some of services implementations. Adds individual transaction management on DAO-s.

task.summary: Creates project structure. Sets up persistance layer datasource and ORM configurations, defines the beans. Implements persistance layer Entities, further can be a subject of chages. Defines DAO-s.
Repairs transaction management. Adds temporary controllers and services in each microservce so to implement distributed system. Some minor changes.
There we go ))) Distributed application with microservices and eureka discovery server hearth beats. Great !
